const Emitter = require('events')

const aboutConfig = require('./config').section
const emtrID = new Emitter();
emtrID.on(aboutConfig.section, function () {
   return 'about'
})


const bckgrdConfig = require('./config').background;
const emtrLightBg = new Emitter();
emtrLightBg.on(bckgrdConfig.lightBg, function () {
  return ''
})


function defaultObj() {
  return {
    id: " ",
    lightBg: undefined,
    lightText: undefined,
    lightTextDesc: undefined,
    topLine: " ",
    headline: "Unlimited Transactions with zero fees",
    description:
      "Get access to our exclusive app that allows you to send unlimited transactions without getting charged any fees",
    buttonLabel: "Get started",
    imgStart: false,
    img: require("../../images/svg-1.svg").default,
    alt: "Car",
    dark: true,
    primary: true,
    darkText: false,
  };
}
